author: Aaron Besecker The Buffalo News (TNS)
title: Goo Goo Dolls will play benefit concert at Town Ballroom next week for FeedMore WNY
text:
The Goo Goo Dolls will perform Nov. 20 at Town Ballroom in a show to benefit FeedMore WNY, the venue announced Monday morning.
